  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You shatter the barriers between dimensions thrusting them into turmoil and madness. The target must make a Charisma saving throw or it can't take Reactions until the jutsu ends and must also roll a d10 at the start of each of its turns; the number rolled determines what happens to the target as shown on the Reality Break Effects table. If used while inside of a pocket dimension created by another jutsu, that dimension collapses on itself, being destroyed, and ejects all creatures and objects in it outside the pocket dimension.</p><img src=\"systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Cheat%20Sheet/Reality%20Break.png\" />",
